OL,4,Cappointed as Victims' Commissioner for
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FA leading Violence Against Women and
OL,8,FGirls (VAWG) campaigner has been
OL,9,Fannounced as London's new Victim's
OL,10,FCommissioner.
OL,12,FAndrea Simon will take up the role of
OL,13,Fchampioning rights of crime victims in
OL,14,Fthe capital, having spent the last two
OL,15,Fdecades advocating women's safety and
OL,16,Fprevention of child trafficking on a
OL,17,Flocal and national scale.
