OL,3,CLeading women's safety campaigner
OL,4,Cappointed as Victims' Commissioner for
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FShe is a founding member of the
OL,8,FMayor's London Policing Board and
OL,9,Fspent five years as the director of
OL,10,Fthe End Violence Against Women (EVAW)
OL,11,Fcoalition.
OL,13,FEVAW brings together more than 160
OL,14,Fwomen's support organisations,
OL,15,Fresearchers and survivors to tackle
OL,16,FVAWG in all its forms.
OL,18,FMs Simon took part in the Angiolini
OL,19,FInquiry, which was set up after the
OL,20,Fmurder of Sarah Everard.
