OL,7,FShe said it was a "privilege" to be
OL,8,Fappointed.
OL,10,F"I've worked to improve responses to
OL,11,Fvictims of some of the most life
OL,12,Fchanging crimes over the past decade,
OL,13,Ffirstly victims of child trafficking
OL,14,Fand exploitation, and then for victims
OL,15,Fof violence against women and girls.
