OL,3,CLeading women's safety campaigner
OL,4,Cappointed as Victims' Commissioner for
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,F"It is critical that all victims
OL,8,Freceive the responses they are
OL,9,Fentitled to when they report crime,
OL,10,Fbut this is too often not the case
OL,11,Fparticularly for those from more
OL,12,Fmarginalised communities.
OL,14,F"I remain committed to working to
OL,15,Ftackling structural barriers to
OL,16,Faccessing justice, and ensuring all
OL,17,Fvictims have their rights respected
OL,18,Fand upheld."
OL,20,FShe will take up the new role in March
OL,21,F2026.
