OL,7,FThe Mayor of London said Andrea will
OL,8,Fbring "an incredible wealth of
OL,9,Fknowledge, experience and passion" to
OL,10,Fthe role.
OL,12,FSir Sadiq Khan added: "Since creating
OL,13,Fthe post of London's Victims'
OL,14,FCommissioner in 2017, we have made
OL,15,Fimportant steps towards ensuring we
OL,16,Fhave a justice system that works for
OL,17,Fall.
